airs in the vast region from the Pacific to the Indian Ocean and beyond.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2022) 0aGeopoliticszAsia. 0aSea control. 70(DE-588)4038301-50(DE-627)1044439520(DE-576)209029420aMeer2gnd 70(DE-588)4056618-30(DE-627)1061543030(DE-576)209118288aStaat2gnd 70(DE-588)4057952-90(DE-627)1061490750(DE-576)209124202aStrategie2gnd 70(DE-588)4072885-70(DE-627)1060939320(DE-576)209188553aInternationale Politik2gnd 70(DE-588)4076605-60(DE-627)1060825230(DE-576)20920236XaRegionalentwicklung2gnd 70(DE-588)4125218-40(DE-627)10574185X0(DE-576)209574747aGroßmacht2gnd 70(DE-588)4125488-00(DE-627)1057398550(DE-576)209576979aInternationales politisches System2gnd 70(DE-588)4156741-90(DE-627)1046090010(DE-576)209829168aGeopolitik2gnd 70(DE-588)4175043-30(DE-627)10536746X0(DE-576)209960949aPolitischer Prozess2gnd 70(DE-588)4191103-90(DE-627)1052446860(DE-576)210071230aZugang2gnd 70(DE-588)4204973-80(DE-627)1051392540(DE-576)210165766aKonzeption2gnd 70(DE-588)4209283-80(DE-627)1043532010(DE-576)210191112aEinflussgröße2gnd 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / Asian.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertLynne Rienner Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311078352040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978162637950340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781626379503423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781626379503/original  a978-3-11-078352-0  Lynne Rienner Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles